#Text=Joey Logano wins his first NASCAR Sprint Cup race of 2016
#Text=Tuesday , June 14 , 2016

#Text=On Sunday , Team Penske driver Joey Logano claimed his first NASCAR Sprint Cup Series win of the 2016 season in the FireKeepers Casino 400 at the Michigan International Speedway in Brooklyn , Michigan .
#Text=The 200-lap race began with Logano starting from the pole position , and featured nine cautions and fourteen lead changes between eight different drivers .
#Text=File photo of Joey Logano , 2015 .
#Text=Image : Sarah Stierch .
#Text=Despite starting first , Logano was quickly overtaken on the first lap by Furniture Row Racing driver Martin Truex Jr .
#Text=Truex led the race until Logano reclaimed the first position on lap ten , a position he would keep until the the first cycle of green flag pit stops around lap 40 .
#Text=Logano 's teammate Brad Keselowski took the lead during the pit stop cycle by staying out on the track .
#Text=Keselowski , low on gasoline , led until a caution came out for a spin by Truex around lap 46 .
#Text=During the caution , Keselowski pitted and returned the lead back to his teammate , who led the race until lap 93 .
#Text=Two other cautions slowed the race between the first caution and lap 93 .
#Text=The first occurred when Kyle Busch 's engine failed around lap 53 , forcing the driver to a last-place finish in the race .
#Text=The other caution was caused by contact between the cars of Chris Buescher , Dale Earnhardt Jr. , and A. J. Allmendinger ten laps later .
#Text=Between laps 93 and 103 , Kyle Larson , Ryan Newman , Keselowski , Jimmie Johnson , and Paul Menard led at least one lap .
#Text=Logano returned to the lead on lap 104 , a few laps before a caution when Jeffrey Earnhardt 's car caught fire .
#Text=After the caution , Logano remained in first until Hendrick Motorsports driver Chase Elliott passed him on lap 117 .
#Text=Elliott kept the lead until lap 149 , when he was briefly passed by Logano .

#Text=Elliott retook the lead for three more laps on lap 150 before returning the lead back to Logano , who led until the seventh caution was called around lap 156 for of a collision between Danica Patrick , Brian Scott , and Casey Mears .
#Text=Logano held the lead on the ensuing restart and led through two more caution periods that were called in the final 50 laps .

#Text=The first began around lap 164 because of a collision involving Johnson , Trevor Bayne , and Ryan Blaney , while the final caution of the race was called with about ten laps remaining after Denny Hamlin suffered a tire puncture on the front straightaway and collided into the SAFER barrier .
#Text=On the final restart , Logano retained the first position and led the remainder of the race to capture the fifteenth win of his career .
#Text=After the race , Logano , who led a race-high of 138 laps , praised his team , saying " Team Penske gave me a great race car .

#Text=Elliott , who finished second in the race , expressed disappointment with his result , claiming he  messed up " by not using the correct gear .

column1: #Text=Larson , Keselowski , and Kevin Harvick completed the top-five finishers , while Carl Edwards finished in the sixth position .
#Text=Tony Stewart finished seventh ahead of Austin Dillon and Jamie McMurray , who finished eighth and ninth .
#Text=Kurt Busch completed the first ten positions with a tenth-place finish .
#Text=In post-race inspection , Larson 's car did not pass laser inspection , prompting NASCAR to impound his car so it can be further evaluated .
#Text=Any possible penalties are to be announced in the next week .
#Text=In the drivers ' championship , Harvick led Kurt Busch and Keselowski with 526 points .
#Text=Edwards and Logano were fourth and fifth with 472 and 455 points .
#Text=Elliott was sixth with 453 , followed by Johnson with 441 .
#Text=Truex was scored eighth ahead of Kyle Busch and Matt Kenseth , who completed the top-ten .
#Text=The 2016 season is scheduled to continue on June 26 with the Toyota/Save Mart 350 at Sonoma Raceway .
